@startuml
title How the BAH routes a message through an intermediary
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #3F3F4A
  ParticipantBorderColor #2C2C34
  ParticipantFontColor white
  LifeLineBorderColor #3F3F4A
  ArrowColor #3F3F4A
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E9E9EC
skinparam noteBorderColor #3F3F4A

participant "Sender" as S
participant "Intermediary\n(routing only)" as I
participant "Receiver" as R

S -> I : BAH (Fr, To, MsgDefIdr) + business message
note over I : reads only the BAH to route;\nneed not parse the payload
I -> R : forwards BAH + business message
R -> R : validates Sgntr, reads MsgDefIdr,\nthen processes the payload
@enduml
